author: Stephanie Elam and Madeline Holcombe, CNN
title: Los Angeles County hospitals say people are waiting too long to seek treatment over coronavirus fears
description: Doctors at some Los Angeles County hospitals say people are waiting too long to seek medical treatment -- including those infected with the coronavirus -- over fears of catching Covid-19, potentially leading to more detrimental effects to their health.
